{
    "publish_date": "2013-08-28T13:01:31.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT16M5S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "LARRY KOSILLA: Today, I&#39;m at\nFMI, which is the Northeastern", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "3.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "vehicle press fleet management\ncompany for GM, BMW, and Mini.", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "6.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When the press need to review\ntheir cars for their", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "9.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "publications, this is where they\ncome to check them out.", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "11.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Coming up on today&#39;s episode,\nwe are going to be talking", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "14.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about one of my biggest OCD\npet peeves, a filthy,", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "15.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "contaminated windshield.", 
            "dur": "1.08", 
            "start": "18.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s all coming up today on this\nepisode of &quot;Drive Clean.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "20.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "24.108", 
            "start": "22.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "LARRY KOSILLA: Today, we&#39;re\nworking on the 2013 CTS-V", 
            "dur": "3.112", 
            "start": "46.904"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sport Wagon press vehicle\nin the limited", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "50.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "edition Stealth Blue.", 
            "dur": "1.375", 
            "start": "53.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this thing is a beast.", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "55.061"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I know it&#39;s a beast because\nit&#39;s got bugs all over", 
            "dur": "2.535", 
            "start": "56.901"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the windshield, which I can\nbarely see through.", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "59.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as most detailers will tell\nyou, it&#39;s a huge pain in", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "61.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the butt to properly\nclean glass.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "65.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s what we&#39;re going to\ntalk about today, all the", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "66.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "steps on removing the\ncontaminants and getting that", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "68.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "perfect shine, so when you&#39;re\ndriving, there&#39;s nothing that", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "72.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re looking through.", 
            "dur": "1.07", 
            "start": "75.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Today, we&#39;re going\nto do just that.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "76.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There are a couple benefits to\nhaving a clean windshield.", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "79.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, obviously, in perfect\nweather, you&#39;re going to have", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "81.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a great looking windshield, and\nyou can see right through", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "84.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it, no problems.", 
            "dur": "0.6", 
            "start": "86.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the big one is during\nbad weather.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "87.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You want to prepare for that.", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "89.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the one thing is when those\nlittle things that are", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "90.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "embedded and jammed in your\nglass, they&#39;re going to catch", 
            "dur": "3.12", 
            "start": "93.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the water, and it&#39;s going to\nstay on your windshield a", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "96.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "little bit longer.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "98.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when you have a nice clean\nsurface, it&#39;s going to fly", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "99.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right off, making it safer\nwhen you&#39;re driving.", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "101.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And another benefit is it\nactually saves wear and tear", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "107.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on your windshield wipers,\nbecause if you have those", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "110.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "things sticking up, biting at\nthe windshield wiper, you&#39;re", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "111.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "going to go through them much\nfaster, and you&#39;re going to", 
            "dur": "2.235", 
            "start": "114.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have reduced visibility.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "116.991"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before we can get started with\ncleaning the glass, it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.412", 
            "start": "122.574"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "important to understand the\ntowels that you&#39;re using.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "124.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we have four of them here.", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "127.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, this is a waffle towel.", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "129.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s really great at\nscraping off the bugs.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "130.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I call this my all-in-one.", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "132.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s a waffle\ntowel because it", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "134.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looks like a waffle.", 
            "dur": "1.13", 
            "start": "136.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then we have our three\nother ones.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "137.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We have a high pile microfiber\ntowel, we have a low pile", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "138.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microfiber towel, and we have\na medium pile microfiber", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "142.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "towel, each of which has\ndifferent uses when", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "145.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cleaning the glass.", 
            "dur": "1.225", 
            "start": "148.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right.", 
            "dur": "0.335", 
            "start": "149.291"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The next thing you want to do\nis pull up the windshield", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "149.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wipers to get them\noff the glass.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "151.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then you&#39;re going to take\nyour glass cleaner.", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "153.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This happens to be Invisible\nGlass by Stoner.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "156.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what you&#39;re going to do\nis give a few squirts.", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "158.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And right now, you&#39;re using\nthat as lubrication.", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "161.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what I like to do is\njust spread it in", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "164.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just a little bit.", 
            "dur": "0.59", 
            "start": "166.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re not actually cleaning\nanything right now.", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "166.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re just getting some\nlubrication, because your next", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "168.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "step is going to be your\nlong reach razor blade.", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "171.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what&#39;s important about\nthis is your angle.", 
            "dur": "3.68", 
            "start": "173.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we&#39;re going to make sure\nthat it&#39;s not too", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "177.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "high and not too low.", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "179.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What this is going to do is it&#39;s\nactually going to shave", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "181.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the glass down.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "183.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And anything that&#39;s sticking up,\nkind of like your whiskers", 
            "dur": "3.25", 
            "start": "184.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "here, it&#39;s going to shave\neverything off.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "187.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s going to get the\nclosest clean that you", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "189.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "possibly can do.", 
            "dur": "0.74", 
            "start": "192.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, there&#39;s a bug\nright there.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "193.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you&#39;ll notice, going in\nshort little strokes, you can", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "194.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "see not too far down\nand not too far up.", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "199.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Right in the middle there.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "202.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you notice, all this little\nwater that&#39;s dripping down", 
            "dur": "3.48", 
            "start": "204.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "here is full of contamination\nand bugs.", 
            "dur": "3.185", 
            "start": "208.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re just going to keep\nmoving along, kind of like", 
            "dur": "4.185", 
            "start": "211.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re plowing the glass,\nif you will.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "215.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sorry, guys.", 
            "dur": "0.32", 
            "start": "228.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is taking-- it&#39;s a\nbig piece of glass.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "228.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now that you&#39;ve razor bladed\nthe glass, take your short", 
            "dur": "3.38", 
            "start": "245.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pile microfiber towel and just\nclean it up real quick just to", 
            "dur": "5.21", 
            "start": "248.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "get all the gunk off.", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "253.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at that.", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "257.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s a clean\npiece of glass.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "259.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Put this to the side.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "262.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re going to add your glass\ncleaner, once again, as", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "264.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lubrication.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "266.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Get that in there.", 
            "dur": "1.425", 
            "start": "270.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I like to spread it around\njust a little bit.", 
            "dur": "4.445", 
            "start": "272.051"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;re going to take your\nclay, lubricate the clay, and", 
            "dur": "5.03", 
            "start": "276.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now you&#39;re going to put a\nlittle bit of pressure.", 
            "dur": "3.46", 
            "start": "281.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Normally on paint, you\ndon&#39;t use pressure.", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "284.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s all about friction.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "287.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But because glass is very hard,\nyou still want to use", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "288.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "some friction, but you can also\nput just a little bit", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "291.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more pressure than you\nwould with paint.", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "294.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, what this is doing is kind\nof like when you have a", 
            "dur": "4.05", 
            "start": "297.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pimple on your face, you&#39;re\ngoing to pull", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "301.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it out of the skin.", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "304.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We shaved it with the razor\nblade, and now you&#39;re just", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "305.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "getting anything that you didn&#39;t\nget with the razor.", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "308.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re going to have really\nclean and fresh glass.", 
            "dur": "5.37", 
            "start": "311.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s take a look.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "316.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah, there&#39;s a bunch of\ngunk right in there.", 
            "dur": "2.596", 
            "start": "317.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, you&#39;re going to\ntake your short pile once", 
            "dur": "3.134", 
            "start": "319.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "again and clean up the mess.", 
            "dur": "3.375", 
            "start": "323.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On to the next step.", 
            "dur": "1.554", 
            "start": "334.382"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, if you were going out for\na drive, this might be good", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "335.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "enough for just going out and\nhaving a Sunday drive.", 
            "dur": "3.05", 
            "start": "338.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you want to go the\nfull steps, this is", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "341.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what you would do.", 
            "dur": "1.05", 
            "start": "343.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this, to remind\nyou, is a regular", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "344.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microfiber cutting pad.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "346.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a little bit thinner\nmicrofiber cutting pad.", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "348.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a glass polishing pad.", 
            "dur": "1.965", 
            "start": "351.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see, it&#39;s\nmuch thinner.", 
            "dur": "2.455", 
            "start": "353.531"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the reason why is glass\nis much harder.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "355.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re not going to need a\nbacking plate to absorb any of", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "358.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that pressure.", 
            "dur": "0.47", 
            "start": "361.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You want it all to go to the\nglass so that you can polish", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "361.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it properly.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "364.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what we&#39;re going to do is\ngrab a machine, put some", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "365.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "product on there, and\nstart polishing.", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "367.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now we&#39;ve got a little bit\nof glass polish on our glass", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "369.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "polishing pad.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "371.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rub it in with our finger.", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "374.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And much like polishing the\npaint, throw the cord over", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "376.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your shoulder.", 
            "dur": "0.375", 
            "start": "378.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re going to work a 2 by 2\narea, which is basically we&#39;re", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "379.121"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "going to go a little bit\nmore than half here.", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "382.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So tap, tap, tap.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "384.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just a little tap.", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "387.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now you&#39;re going to turn\nit on 2 and spread it in.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "389.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Turn it off.", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "400.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now boost it all the way up\nto 6 on your DA polisher.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "401.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re going to put some\npressure down and just work it", 
            "dur": "2.542", 
            "start": "404.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in like you would paint.", 
            "dur": "3.088", 
            "start": "406.808"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here, I&#39;m using glass polish and\na glass polishing pad from", 
            "dur": "3.99", 
            "start": "409.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Griot&#39;s Garage.", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "413.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Also, notice that I&#39;m using a\nPorter Cable DA polisher along", 
            "dur": "3.59", 
            "start": "415.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with a backing plate with no\ncushion and a glass polishing", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "418.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pad with no cushion either.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "422.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The combination of no-foam\ncushions increases the power", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "424.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "applied to the glass from the\nmachine and subsequently", 
            "dur": "3.57", 
            "start": "428.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "allows me to use what&#39;s regarded\nas a less powerful", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "431.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "polisher according to\ntoday&#39;s standards.", 
            "dur": "1.795", 
            "start": "434.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once you&#39;re done polishing the\nglass, there&#39;s going to be a", 
            "dur": "2.291", 
            "start": "442.895"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bit of residue.", 
            "dur": "0.7", 
            "start": "445.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s when you take your\nhigh pile microfiber towel,", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "445.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;re just going to scoop\nall this off, like this.", 
            "dur": "5.54", 
            "start": "448.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Flip it over a few times.", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "454.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s a nice shine on this,\nbut we&#39;ve got a few more steps", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "457.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to go through.", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "460.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now that I picked off all\nthat residue that&#39;s in there,", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "462.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re going to go\nback to your low", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "465.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pile microfiber towel.", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "467.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now we&#39;re just going to clean\noff all the edges and make", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "470.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sure that it&#39;s still\nlooking good.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "472.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s no leftover polish.", 
            "dur": "3.338", 
            "start": "474.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you can actually feel\nthe difference.", 
            "dur": "2.402", 
            "start": "477.794"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s very smooth right now\ncompared to when I started.", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "480.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now that we&#39;re done with the\npolishing, we&#39;re going to", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "492.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "do one more quick clean to\nremove any of the polish.", 
            "dur": "3.875", 
            "start": "494.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re going to take your low\npile microfiber towel and work", 
            "dur": "3.965", 
            "start": "498.111"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it in again.", 
            "dur": "0.86", 
            "start": "502.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And one of the big questions I\nget is about ammonia in the", 
            "dur": "4.01", 
            "start": "502.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "glass cleaner.", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "506.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ammonia is typically a\nhome-based glass cleaning", 
            "dur": "4.16", 
            "start": "508.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "product, because there&#39;s lots of\ngrime on your house windows", 
            "dur": "3.66", 
            "start": "512.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and things like that.", 
            "dur": "0.7", 
            "start": "516.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And ammonia is a great\ndegreaser.", 
            "dur": "1.979", 
            "start": "517.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But in the automotive\nindustry, you", 
            "dur": "2.451", 
            "start": "519.005"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "don&#39;t really need it.", 
            "dur": "0.79", 
            "start": "521.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s kind of a concern\nwhen you have window tints,", 
            "dur": "4.73", 
            "start": "522.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because sometimes it adversely\naffects the window tint.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "526.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we don&#39;t really\nneed ammonia.", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "529.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And Invisible Glass by\nStoner is a perfect", 
            "dur": "5.22", 
            "start": "531.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "solution for that.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "536.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So here we go.", 
            "dur": "0.46", 
            "start": "538.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Looks pretty good.", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "538.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now we&#39;re on to putting a really\nstrong coating on this", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "541.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "glass, and we&#39;ll move\nto the interior.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "544.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My next step is to\nadd a hydrophobic", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "547.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "coating to the glass.", 
            "dur": "1.21", 
            "start": "548.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, most people know Rain-X.\nBut there&#39;s tons of other", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "550.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "longer-lasting products\nout there.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "553.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what you do is you add\na few squirts to a foam", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "555.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "applicator pad, or this\nlittle piece of", 
            "dur": "2.07", 
            "start": "558.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "foam that I have here.", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "560.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What you&#39;re going to do is\nyou&#39;re going to use small", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "561.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "circular motions.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "564.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think by now most\nof you know I&#39;m", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "565.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not crazy about circles.", 
            "dur": "1.22", 
            "start": "567.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But on glass, because you&#39;re\ntrying to penetrate the top", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "568.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "layer of that glass, circles\nis a good option.", 
            "dur": "3.87", 
            "start": "571.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Short, overlapping motions.", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "575.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;re just going\nto work the--", 
            "dur": "0.98", 
            "start": "579.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here, I demonstrated using\nRain-X because it&#39;s the", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "580.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cheapest, easiest, and quite\nfrankly, the most", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "582.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "familiar one out there.", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "584.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nowadays, there are dozens of\nother coatings, so pick the", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "586.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "brand you&#39;re most comfortable\nwith.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "589.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "However, the application process\nis basically the same.", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "590.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A few more squirts.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "593.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now the product is dry.", 
            "dur": "1.659", 
            "start": "609.802"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What you want to do is give just\na few little squirts of", 
            "dur": "3.45", 
            "start": "611.461"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your glass cleaner.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "614.911"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you want to take off\nthe top layer of", 
            "dur": "2.795", 
            "start": "616.381"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this hydrophobic product.", 
            "dur": "1.065", 
            "start": "619.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;ll see it just\ncomes right off.", 
            "dur": "2.565", 
            "start": "620.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But sometimes it&#39;s nice to add a\nlittle bit of glass cleaner,", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "622.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because this can dry to a little\nbit of a hard haze, I", 
            "dur": "3.62", 
            "start": "625.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like to say.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "628.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now you want to go, add a few\nmore squirts now that it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "3.89", 
            "start": "631.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "off, and really clean the\nwindshield nicely.", 
            "dur": "5.646", 
            "start": "635.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, my last little step I like\nto do is I use the high", 
            "dur": "5.754", 
            "start": "641.202"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microfiber towel, I flip\nit over, do one", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "646.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quick little squirt.", 
            "dur": "3.23", 
            "start": "650.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this will get off\nany little streaks.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "653.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The idea is to move your head\nand catch the light and see if", 
            "dur": "4.46", 
            "start": "656.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you see any odd streaks, because\nthere&#39;s nothing worse", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "661.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than driving down the\nstreet and seeing", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "664.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one line going across.", 
            "dur": "1.845", 
            "start": "666.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s super annoying.", 
            "dur": "2.281", 
            "start": "668.131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the microfiber towel is\nreally good at getting those", 
            "dur": "2.794", 
            "start": "670.412"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "little spots.", 
            "dur": "1.456", 
            "start": "673.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This looks good to me.", 
            "dur": "1.639", 
            "start": "674.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The last thing you want\nto do is pull up", 
            "dur": "1.885", 
            "start": "676.301"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your windshield wipers.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "678.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, my medium pile microfiber\ntowel, I&#39;ll take a little bit", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "680.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of glass cleaner, and I&#39;ll\nsquirt it in a straight line", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "683.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just like that.", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "687.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m going to take my fingers\nand pinch the rubber", 
            "dur": "4.7", 
            "start": "688.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just like that.", 
            "dur": "0.99", 
            "start": "693.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So take it inside of the\nmicrofiber towel, hold this", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "694.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "end, pinch, and wipe\nall the way down.", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "698.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now you&#39;re getting off\nall the junk that&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "702.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "accumulated on there.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "704.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now that your windshield is\nclean, now your wipers can be", 
            "dur": "4.38", 
            "start": "705.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clean, too.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "710.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now that we cleaned the outside\nof the glass, it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "712.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "important to focus on the\ninside of the glass.", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "713.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of the big problems that I\nsee a lot of people run into", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "716.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is they come from the\ndriver&#39;s side seat.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "718.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if you&#39;re sitting in here\nand you want to reach these", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "720.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "areas, you have to kind of\nbattle or fight the steering", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "723.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wheel, which is not\na great option.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "726.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what you need to do is come\nfrom the passenger-side seat.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "728.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What you want to do is put your\nleft knee right in the", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "731.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "middle of the seat.", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "733.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And eventually, you&#39;re\ngoing to put your", 
            "dur": "1.09", 
            "start": "735.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "left hand right here.", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "736.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But before you do that, you&#39;re\ngoing to take your cleaner,", 
            "dur": "4.65", 
            "start": "737.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "two squirts on a rag.", 
            "dur": "2.106", 
            "start": "741.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what you&#39;re going to do is\ntake your glass cleaning towel", 
            "dur": "4.094", 
            "start": "744.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and get all the way\nin the corner.", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "748.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And go up and down, and then go", 
            "dur": "4.27", 
            "start": "750.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "horizontally to get in there.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "754.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you notice, I put\nmy right hand here.", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "757.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as I go and clean that\ncorner, I flip it upside down", 
            "dur": "3.79", 
            "start": "760.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and put my left hand so that I\ncan get stable before I get", 
            "dur": "5.34", 
            "start": "764.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all the way to the edge.", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "769.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, if you&#39;re working before\nfrom the seat, you just", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "770.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wouldn&#39;t be able to reach it.", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "773.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of the big things that I\nget a lot in emails is, how", 
            "dur": "3.79", 
            "start": "775.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "come I don&#39;t spray the\nglass just like this?", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "778.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the answer is when you spray\nthe glass, there&#39;s mist", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "781.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that comes down on\nthe dashboard.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "784.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And because we&#39;re all OCD\nwatching these videos, is you", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "786.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "want to go, and you wipe\nthe dashboard.", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "789.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the big thing is\nwe&#39;re going to", 
            "dur": "1.27", 
            "start": "791.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have it nice and clean.", 
            "dur": "1.27", 
            "start": "792.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s going to be dressings\non there sometimes.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "793.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the plastic itself does what\nwe call gassing out, so", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "796.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s going to release all\nthese plasticizers.", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "799.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What you do is when you wipe it\nand you put it back on the", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "802.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "glass, it&#39;s going to\nsmear everywhere.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "804.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And basically, you&#39;re\ngoing to be what we", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "806.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "call chasing the glass.", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "808.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s going to keep pushing it\naround and never get it clean.", 
            "dur": "3.66", 
            "start": "809.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Two squirts.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "813.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Put it in your right hand Take\nyour right hand, flip it", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "814.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "upside down, and get\ninto the corners.", 
            "dur": "4.06", 
            "start": "817.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s what&#39;s going to allow\nyou to clean the glass", 
            "dur": "3.12", 
            "start": "821.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "properly without blowing\nout your back.", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "824.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Cleaning the inside of the\nwindshield is pretty", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "832.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hard on your body.", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "833.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And these little tools\nactually make", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "835.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it easier for you.", 
            "dur": "0.71", 
            "start": "836.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is, I don&#39;t know,\n$5 or $10.", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "837.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What you do is you can just\nslide it down the glass, and", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "839.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;ll reach the far areas that\nsome people can&#39;t reach.", 
            "dur": "5.15", 
            "start": "842.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they actually work\npretty good.", 
            "dur": "1.14", 
            "start": "847.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just get a microfiber, one or\ntwo squirts, reach it down", 
            "dur": "4.94", 
            "start": "848.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there, and now that&#39;s all you\nhave to focus on is the top", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "853.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "part of the glass, not\nthe lower part.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "857.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This will save your back.", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "859.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, if your car has a door\nframe like this one, all the", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "861.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "way to the top, you&#39;re going to\nput the window down a few", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "863.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "inches, take your towel, pinch\nit, and just get the top of", 
            "dur": "5.01", 
            "start": "865.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the window before you\nput it back up.", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "870.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we got all the\njunk off that.", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "874.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pull it back up.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "876.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then you&#39;re going to do\na few squirts here, a few", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "877.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "squirts there.", 
            "dur": "1.736", 
            "start": "880.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;re going to work\nthe edges first.", 
            "dur": "2.304", 
            "start": "881.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One edge to one edge, up\nall the way around.", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "884.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;re going to go\nright in the middle.", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "887.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One, two, three, like this.", 
            "dur": "2.625", 
            "start": "888.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then go back the\nopposite direction.", 
            "dur": "3.325", 
            "start": "891.171"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Flip it over, dry side.", 
            "dur": "2.255", 
            "start": "894.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now you&#39;ve got a nice,\nclean piece of glass.", 
            "dur": "3.472", 
            "start": "899.774"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Repeat that process for the rest\nof the car, and you&#39;ll be", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "903.246"
        }, 
